title: Book Reviews
----
<p>I regularly review books for some of the organisations which I'm a member of. I'm also happy to review books for other publications free of charge, on the proviso that I get to keep the book afterwards. Please <a href="/contact/">contact me</a> if you'd like me to review a particular text.</p>
<h3>FLOSS UK Newsletter</h3>
<p>Published quarterly, the <a href="http://www.flossuk.org/Newsletter">FLOSS UK newsletter</a> (previously UKUUG newsletter) is one of the publications which I regularly contribute to. I have also edited the newsletter since August 2014.</p>
